**Week 3-4: Platform Design & Setup**
Our development team—senior tech specialists and fresh engineers trained in C#—design the architecture. We create the interface. We set up the environment.

**Week 5-8: Data Integration**
We set up automated pipelines for Git metrics. We start curating and validating manual data. We run tests. We make sure everything's accurate.

**Week 9-12: Launch & Optimization**
We deploy the platform. We train the data stewards. We monitor performance. We optimize based on feedback.

[PAUSE]

So, timeline: 12 weeks. About 3 months from today to a live, functioning platform.

[VOICE - Realistic]

Is that fast? Yes. Is it ambitious? Yes. Is it doable? Absolutely, with your support."

---

### SPEAKER NOTES - Implementation Timeline

