### SPEAKER NOTES - Closing

- **Recap:** Hit the five key points quickly
- **Emotion:** Build from logic to emotion
- **Call to Action:** Make the ask one more time
- **Warmth:** End on a human note
- **Silence:** Let the closing land—don't rush to leave

